    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use counter punch with ranged attacks, except that instead of readying an action to make an attack against the next enemy who makes a melee attack roll against you before the beginning of your next round, you ready an action to make an attack against the next enemy who makes an attack roll within your first range increment before the beginning of your next round. You may select additional triggers for counter punch as normal, except that they must be within your first range increment in order to trigger your counter punch.</p>\n",
